OL,3,CSwimmers' campaign for weekly testing
OL,4,Cto eradicate sewage pollution in river
OL,6,FSwimmers in Devon are campaigning to
OL,7,Fclean up the River Dart.
OL,9,FFriends of the Dart say they are fed
OL,10,Fup with the "constant stream of sewage
OL,11,Freleases, road and agricultural run-
OL,12,Foff".
OL,14,FThe Environment Agency currently tests
OL,15,Fat four sites along the 47-mile river
OL,16,Fbetween May and September.
OL,18,FThe community initiative is hoping to
OL,19,Fraise #30,000 so weekly testing can be
OL,20,Fdone at seven sites, all year round.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
