OL,3,CSwimmers' campaign for weekly testing
OL,4,Cto eradicate sewage pollution in river
OL,6,FNicky Rajska, director of Friends of
OL,7,Fthe Dart, said: "Each single test, for
OL,8,Ftwo bacterias, costs #30, so if we
OL,9,Fwant to do that weekly and we want to
OL,10,Fdo that at multiple sites, that amount
OL,11,Fadds up.
OL,13,F"The testing is important is that the
OL,14,Ftesting gives accountability. It shows
OL,15,Fwhere the sewage is coming from it
OL,16,Fshows the source of it, it shows what
OL,17,Fit is.
OL,19,F"The EA at the moment just test in the
OL,20,Fbathing water season. So if we want
OL,21,Fchange, this is the way to do it.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
