OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F433A1724318695
OL,3,CSwimmers' campaign for weekly testing
OL,4,Cto eradicate sewage pollution in river
OL,6,F"No-one else is doing it so we've
OL,7,Fstepped into that space and we are
OL,8,Fwilling to do it."
OL,10,FDr Joanna Rose, who regularly swims at
OL,11,Fa bathing spot in Totnes, hopes the
OL,12,Fconsistent testing will make a
OL,13,Fdifference.
OL,15,FShe said: "Our whole family and our
OL,16,Fneighbours have become seriously ill,
OL,17,Fvomiting for 24 hours or more. We're
OL,18,Ftrying to find ways to swim where we
OL,19,Fdon't get sick.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
