OL,3,CSwimmers' campaign for weekly testing
OL,4,Cto eradicate sewage pollution in river
OL,6,F"There were times in the summer when
OL,7,Fapparently the pollution became more
OL,8,Fconcentrated. We're told to not swim
OL,9,Fwhen it rains too much. But also not
OL,10,Fto swim when it hasn't rained.
OL,12,F"So we're trying to juggle all these
OL,13,Fdifference circumstances. So it's
OL,14,Flike, so when can I swim?"
OL,16,FAnother swimmer said: "It's not just
OL,17,Fswimming, people use the River Dart
OL,18,Ffor rowing, canoeing, walking, paddle
OL,19,Fboarding, boating.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
