OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F433A1724318695
OL,3,CSwimmers' campaign for weekly testing
OL,4,Cto eradicate sewage pollution in river
OL,6,F"You know there's so many activities
OL,7,Fdone of this river and it's just
OL,8,Fdelightful when it's clean but at the
OL,9,Fmoment it feels a bit uncomfortable
OL,10,Fgoing in.
OL,12,F"It's not something you can do in many
OL,13,Fplaces, it's a beautiful place to swim
OL,14,Fas well. Anyone can come down here.
OL,15,FAnd that's an opportunity we should
OL,16,Fpreserve," another added.
OL,18,FSouth West Water (SWW) has said it is
OL,19,Finvesting #33 million into storm
OL,20,Foverflows at the four new bathing
OL,21,Fwater sites on the River Dart by 2030.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
