OL,3,CSwimmers' campaign for weekly testing
OL,4,Cto eradicate sewage pollution in river
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the water company
OL,7,Fsaid: "There are a wide range of
OL,8,Ffactors which can affect river water
OL,9,Fquality, including agricultural and
OL,10,Furban pollution.
OL,12,F"We recognise that to improve the
OL,13,Fquality of our rivers, we all need to
OL,14,Fplay our part."
OL,16,FDavid Reed, Conservative MP for
OL,17,FExmouth and Exeter East, said:
OL,18,F"Firstly, I want to express how upset
OL,19,Fand angry people are.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
