OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F433A1724318695
OL,3,CSwimmers' campaign for weekly testing
OL,4,Cto eradicate sewage pollution in river
OL,6,F"We've had two major pipes burst since
OL,7,FI've been elected. It's had a huge
OL,8,Fimpact on tourism and people haven't
OL,9,Fbeen able to use their local beach.
OL,11,F"I've called on South West Water to
OL,12,Fbring forward their structural
OL,13,Fengineering fund to fix these issues.
OL,15,F"They're going to make a four-week
OL,16,Fanalysis of the network. They need to
OL,17,Fbe doing their engagements with local
OL,18,Fpeople and the cameras.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
