OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F433A1724318695
OL,3,CSwimmers' campaign for weekly testing
OL,4,Cto eradicate sewage pollution in river
OL,6,F"I've stepped in because the situation
OL,7,Fdictates it. The narrative has been
OL,8,Flost on this. South West Water need to
OL,9,Ftell people what's going on and what's
OL,10,Fbeing done to fix it. The trust is
OL,11,Fcompletely gone.
OL,13,F"There is no overnight fix to this and
OL,14,Fthis is going to take time to fix. The
OL,15,Ffact that trust is so low and there
OL,16,Fare so many different narratives about
OL,17,Fwhat's happening is a failure on their
OL,18,Fpart.
OL,20,F"Actions speak louder than words, get
OL,21,Fon with the job."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
